      "span_text": "When the TSV MIS is in accumulation region, the electrical field is confined in the SiO 2 liner and the TSV capacitance is equal to C ox . When TSV MIS is in depletion region, the electrical field can penetrate into the substrate, and the TSV capacitance is equal to C ox in series with C dep . (C ox is the capacitance of the SiO 2 liner, C dep is the capacitance of the depletion region). Accordingly, an analytical formula for depletion capacitance is introduced for the large signal and nonlinear capacitance [CITATION_1] ."
